title: Skype usage reach in the United States 2018 , by age group
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Reach, with a total of 7 data points. The chart has 3 significant trends.
The longest trend is slightly positive which exists from 25-34 to 55-64.
Correspondingly, the next significant trend is extremely negative which exists from 55-64 to 75+.
Differently, the next significant trend is extremely negative which exists from 18-24 to 25-34.
